---
 
## Security Note — Firewall :3000 in Production
 
OpenClaw's gateway on :3000 accepts requests directly.  
In production, **firewall :3000** so only GEL (:3100) can reach it.  
Otherwise requests bypass all governance.
 
In dev: both ports are open. That's fine for testing.
 
---
 
## What the `current/openclaw/` Folder Is
 
The `current/openclaw/src/index.ts` file in this project is a **GEL test harness** —  
a lightweight Express stub that runs on :3000 and accepts GEL-forwarded requests  
when real OpenClaw is not installed.
 
It is NOT OpenClaw. It does NOT make real model calls.  
It is useful for testing that GEL governance works correctly before setting up OpenClaw.
 
When you install and run real OpenClaw:
- Real OpenClaw listens on :3000
- The test harness is no longer needed
- GEL's behavior doesn't change — it proxies the same way either direction
 
---
 
